Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(2003年7月4日)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我说说那个女孩吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So tell me about the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(几周前)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实如果不是因为你 我原本不可能遇见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}actually never would have met her if it weren't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以说这都是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So in a way, this is kind of all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理 请和我解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please enlighten me, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要我完全说实话 艾尔舒医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm being a hundred percent totally honest with you here, Dr. Altschul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些每周的咨询并非我最爱的午后活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these weekly sessions are not exactly my favorite afternoon activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(失踪人口)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去年秋天起 我妈同意我自己开车到城里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But last fall, my mom started to let me drive into the city myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说咨询结束后 我可以自由地闲逛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which meant, when we were done here, I was free to wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(A1唱片店)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是高中同窗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We went to high school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算同窗 她高我一级\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not together. She was a year ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经毕业了 在纽约大学读书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}already graduated and started at NYU.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不算是朋友 但她就是个令我难忘的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like we were friends or anything, but she's just hard to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 请问你是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. How do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该都上过花山高中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we both went to Flower Hill High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 我仍然在那里读书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I mean I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯威斯巴格 叫我查理就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles Weisbarger. Charlie's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯 你怎么跑到这了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Charles, what are you doing all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说...大家跑到这里不都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean I-- What's anyone doing out here just
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃离长岛 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}getting the hell off Long Island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案正确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your doctor's appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是那种医生 - 是 可不是嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not that kind of doctor. - Yeah. No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人来城里 绝对是来看心理医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're coming into the city solo. It's got to be a shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家长要分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are your parents splitting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次和心理健康 专业人士打交道的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's when I had my first brush with a mental health professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸去年九月去世了 所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My dad died last September. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想看我的杂志吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you wanna see my zine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么杂志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's a zine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是半个自传\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's semi-autobiographical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(千舞之地)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 但又不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, but not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你好 我叫怪胎)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的摄影 插画 音乐评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My photography, illustrations, music reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识这些乐队的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These guys I know are in this band,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前事追溯)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想记录他们的活动 文化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'm trying to document their whole scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们对拍照和隐私很敏感 所以我记录得很隐晦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but they're kind of weird about photos and privacy, so it's thinly veiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改了名字以保护当事人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Names changed to protect the guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好棒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们花山的孩子应该互相支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think us Flower Hill kids need to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 查尔斯 你就是我的课题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From now on, Charles, you're gonna be my project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周我从你这里离开后 我们都会见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We met up every week after I left here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你可以说 我真正的教育是从那时开始的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I guess that's when you could say my real education began.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(迈克布隆伯格 纽约领袖)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(鲁迪朱利安尼 市长)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(靴子)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很帅气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她身边 你实际上是无法感到悲伤的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was physically impossible to be sad when she was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和许多其他很酷的音乐很像 但有点...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like a lot of other cool things, but it's kind of like--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道 还没完呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I know. It's not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《黄铜战术》是前事追溯的唯一专辑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brass Tactics was the only album Ex Post Facto made
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比利三棍解散乐队前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before Billy Three-Sticks broke up the band,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有走红就解散了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before they ever had a chance to get big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但奇怪的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in a weird way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只做了一张专辑这点 让这张专辑更加特别了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fact that they only made one album makes it even more special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你必须拥有一张 - 不 我没有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You must own it. - No, I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概可以在LimeWire上下载吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I could probably just download it off LimeWire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯 那会让乐队 失去他们辛苦赚的版税钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles, that would deprive the band of their well-earned royalties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我送你 - 不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm buying. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来 这是在纽约度过秋天的绝佳方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds like a wonderful way to spend autumn in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来就不是了 虽然我猜那只能怪我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until it wasn't. Although I guess there's no one to blame for that but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈 当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my mom, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说你整夜不归家 然后在早上开车回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you tell me you stayed out all night and then drove home in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没穿上衣 因为宿醉呕吐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shirtless and vomiting from a hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的原话不是那样 但是 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well-- I didn't exactly say it like that, but yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年前夕总是会发生些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, New Year's Eve, shit happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你母亲决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you think your mother's decision
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你关禁闭六个月不合理吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to ground you for six months was unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和我妈无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't about my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是关于小萨 关于我爱她 以及也许她也爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about Sam and how I love her and that maybe she loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And like, I don't know. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还没想清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But before I could even figure all that out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法再见她了 所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't allowed to see her anymore, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的故事就这样中止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My story just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理 这点很鼓舞人 你可以这么清楚地诉说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's encouraging, Charlie, that you can speak so clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about your sense of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wish you would talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也这样感性地谈论失去父亲的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the loss of your father in the same perceptive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1998年 坎托菲茨杰拉德赛)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得有没有可能 通过专注于萨曼莎的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think it's possible that focusing on Samantha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你借此回避自己关于父亲的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a way of deflecting your feelings about your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- ...飞机的 真的  - 绝对是737\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ...from the plane. Really? - It's definitely a 737.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(永远缅怀)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人撞上了世界贸易中心 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody hit the World Trade Center. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对你来说更容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's easier to feel the way you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为一个住在几公里外 生机勃勃的年轻女子情绪波动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about a vibrant young woman living a few miles away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是去处理 失去你父亲而造成的深重 永久创伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than it is to process the deep, permanent loss of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...正爆炸 这里有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...exploded right now. We got people all over here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在街道中央\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}down in the middle of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次撞击 刚撞上另一栋楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another hit. It just hit another building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架飞机撞上了 曼哈顿下城的世界贸易中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two aircraft crashed into the World Trade Center in lower Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等... - 发生了爆炸...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, wait, wait. - We've got an explosion--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊 一定是个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. It must be a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪里  - 不 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where? - No, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪里  - 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where? - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有言语可描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 查理 是爸爸 出了点事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Charlie, it's Dad. Something's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概已经在新闻上看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've probably seen it on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我回不了家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想要你知道我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want you to know I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 医生 这一整件事 没有任何“容易”可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me, doc, there's nothing easy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂 - 嗨 陌生人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello. - Hey, stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在关禁闭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still grounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案最好是“没有” 因为前事追溯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The answer better be "no" because Ex Post Facto,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我不在的这段时间 他们仍是你最爱的乐队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who I hope in my absence is still your favorite band,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会在4号开重聚演唱会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is reuniting for a concert on the Fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比利三棍不能算重聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it's not really a reunion without Billy Three-Sticks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也改了名 但是会表演所有歌曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they changed the name, but they're playing all their songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很传奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's going to be legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果错过 你一定不会放过自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd basically kill yourself if you missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 查尔斯 在吗 你听到了吗  - 是的...当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello, Charles? Are you in? - Yes. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...对 我不会错过的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- Yeah, I wouldn't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 可是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没有可是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们这么久没聊过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just we haven't really talked in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我试过打给你 但你没回电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I tried calling you, but you never called back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 抱歉 我只是觉得我没什么可说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, sorry, I just didn't feel like I had anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 如果我和你的禁足有任何关系 那我深表抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm sorry for any role that I may have played in your incarceration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 那段日子真的是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? That was a time of real...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长和内省的机会 所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}real growth and introspection, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的 烂透了 我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm kidding. It sucked. I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话让我好难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也让我很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it also makes me very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想死你了 查尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I've missed the hell out of you, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我得挂了 但7月4号活动详情稍后再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I got to go, but details about the Fourth of July shenanigans are to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜拜 - 尼基 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bye. - Nicky, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 小萨 走啦 - 走...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sammy. Let's go. - Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要命 你们放火烧教堂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Holy shit! You guys torched a fucking church?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们做了什么 为罪孽忏悔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd you think we were doing? Confessing our sins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上车 走啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get in the car. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 女士们 快点 磨蹭什么呢  - 你们做了什...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ladies. Come on. What are we doing? - Why did you do--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么以教堂为目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you target a fucking church?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 尼基去哪了  - 不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Nicky? Where's Nicky? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等 不能落下尼基 - 他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, we can't leave without Nicky. - He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 尼基 - 你们做了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nicky! - What the fuck did you guys do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 走 快点啊 - 快点 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go. Come on! - Come on. Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们不能抛下你 - 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can't leave without you. - Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a thing of beauty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 踩油门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go! Step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 美丽广阔的苍穹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O beautiful for spacious skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金黄的稻浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For amber waves of grain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壮丽的紫山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For purple mountain majesties
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硕果累累的平原之上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Above the fruited plain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}America--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮什玛古普帕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nishima Guptpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特汉密尔顿斯维尼兰普莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cate Hamilton-Sweeney Lamplighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 保重 - 非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take care. - Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 对 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Yep. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特汉密尔顿斯维尼兰普莱特 她的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cate Hamilton-Sweeney Lamplighter, her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 能指给我看是哪位吗  - 为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you point her out for me? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我可能认识她的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I might know her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你认识汉密尔顿斯维尼家的人  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know a Hamilton-Sweeney? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人脉 那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impressive. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了 她会很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll be great. She'll love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但下次换你家 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's your place next time, like, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不好意思 打扰一下 - 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Excuse me. Sorry. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想介绍一下自己 墨瑟古德曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to introduce myself. Mercer Goodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会 我是...你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice to meet you. I'm-- Are--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是凯特的老师吗  - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you one of Cate's teachers? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个朋友 是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a friend of--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他可能是你兄弟 威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he might be your brother. William.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 快点 孩子们在等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, come on. Kids are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我答应他们让他们吃意大利雪糕 - 是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I may have promised them gelato. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 现在不太方便聊 但是很高兴...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, now is not a great time, but it was really nice--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴认识你 古德曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was really great to meet you, Mr. Goodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她终于睡着了 她好激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's asleep, finally. She was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 你看起来有点心不在焉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything okay with you? You seem a little distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 只是我担心威尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine. It's just I'm worried about Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 他最近不在状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, he's just not himself these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前很喜欢放假前最后一天 而我就是不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He used to love the last day of school, and I just, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他以前喜欢过很多东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. He used to love a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baseball cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宠物小精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宠物小精灵 他的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pokémon. His parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个阶段 他是个好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a phase. He's a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(蕾根)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他在对你洒谎)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要不要聊聊你背着我出轨的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we gonna talk about how you've been cheating on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 出轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯 你靠撒谎 洗脱自己罪名的机会已经没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith, the window where you could bullshit your way out of this has closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她给我写了张字条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wrote me a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我本来就有所怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that I didn't already suspect though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候开始听 放荡乐团的歌 她是25岁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since when do you listen to The Libertines? What is she, 25?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想聊 那我们就聊 但别说得好像这都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want to talk, let's talk. But don't act like this is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记提我背着你出轨那部分了 我都不知道我有个男友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I missed the part where I cheated on you. I had no idea that I had a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 有时感觉你也没有丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, sometimes it feels like you don't have a husband either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她觉得你令人着迷吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does she find you fascinating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是个自由的灵魂 特别有灵动的气质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she so free-spirited and totally fucking alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 算是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does she have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有两个孩子吗 生病的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does she have two kids? A sick father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 吉斯 我曾是那个女孩 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, Keith, I was that girl. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是那个女孩 我掐死了她 好让我们拥有现在的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was that girl, and I strangled her so that we could have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古德曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Goodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 很高兴赶上你在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, I'm glad I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚打算给孩子的老师送份礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just dropping off a gift to my kid's teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们可以继续 之前的谈话或是重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I thought we could finish our conversation or start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 威廉是我的朋友 是一位好友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, William is a friend. A good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可能也没那么好 毕竟在那天之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although maybe not that good, since until the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道他有姐妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know he had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好多年没见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we haven't seen each other in years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不知道 他是不是还住在城里 还是死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I didn't know if he was living in the city still or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我松了一口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想换个地方聊吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like to go somewhere we can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很想 但是我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would love that more than you know. But I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去家里见搬运工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm meeting movers at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家是最烦心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moving, that's always the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 尤其是未经计划的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, especially when it's unplanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望一切顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, everything's okay I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一切都不顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, everything is shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多谢关心 你很善良\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But thanks for asking. You're very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果你在4号前见到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, listen, if you see him, before the Fourth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给他这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would you give him this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 告诉他我很想他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Just tell him I miss him and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a lot has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 告诉他我今年真的需要他陪伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, just tell him I really need him there this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很欢迎你来 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I would love for you to come, Mercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a pleasure meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴威廉身边有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad William's got someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(威廉哈密尔顿斯维尼)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Happy birthday, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 这些插画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my gosh. These illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this-- This is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的恋爱时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is our courtship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以用这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布鲁诺的小屋的那个周末 这是我的艺术汇演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The weekend at Bruno's cabin. This is my art show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们在屋顶上坐着谈天的 那些夜晚 然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is just all those nights we sat up on the roof, just talking, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 和自恋狂艺术家同居 总要有些好处的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Gotta be some upside to living with a narcissistic artist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 来 打开 里面有真的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Let's go. Open it. There's a real present inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉 我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}William. Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 你没有必要送我这么奢侈的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truly, you really did not have to get me something so extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一项对你未来的投资\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as an investment in your future,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它算是挺便宜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it came pretty cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我生日时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去一趟工作室 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna go to the studio for a little bit. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在晚餐前回家 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will be home before dinner. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 你可以安装你的新电脑 可以开始写你的新小说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, you can set up your new computer and you can start that new novel of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有怎样看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not looking at you in any particular way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这是我离开家后的第一个生日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just it is my first birthday away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你已经提过几次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, as you've mentioned a couple times now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天没达到你的预期 那我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry if today is falling short of whatever you had in your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不觉得你仍把乔治亚 称为家这一点很暴露你的想法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but does it strike you as revealing that you still refer to Georgia as home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 也就是我的家乡 至少我仍然会聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Home, as in where I came from. At least I still talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是一个开诚布公的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you are just a man of transparency and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么向你父母描述我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you describe me to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你的室友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? Your roommate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 你不懂 这没那么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, you don't understand. It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他们还是对你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For them or for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我这和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please just tell me this has nothing to do with that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你一有机会就拱到我面前的... - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- fucking envelope that you keep shoving... - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- ...那封信无关 - 威尔 你打算打开它吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ...into my field of vision. - Will, are you ever going to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你家人写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is from your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的是它是怎么进入我们公寓的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want to know is how it got into our apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的是为什么你不和他们说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want to know is why you don't talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们那么... - 有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They're so-- - Rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想说友善 至少你姐姐是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was gonna say nice. At least your sister is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是成年人了 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're grown men, Merce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过生日对我们的年龄来说有点幼稚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Birthdays are a little ridiculous at our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(贝尔与塞巴斯蒂安 《阿拉伯皮带男孩》)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 你在里面太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry up. You've been in there way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在里面太久了 - 你担心过多 没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's been in there way too long. - You worry too much. It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你都装满了  你说我爸不会注意到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. You filled up that whole thing? You said my dad wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会的 而且你说了 他现在都不怎么工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't. Plus, you said he doesn't even work much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他也不需要 - 该死的 索尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not like he needs it. - Fuck, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没有受害者的罪行 我从没来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a victimless crime. I was never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从没来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coming with?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事 今晚见吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got some shit to do. I'll see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(宇宙龙烟火)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们没闯大祸 你拿了好多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope we didn't just fuck up. You took a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爸是个废物酒鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her dad's a washed-up drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 但他和小萨很亲近 她知道那东西有多危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but he and Sam are close. And she knows how dangerous that shit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(美妙烟火)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我正希望你打来 也许你准备好聊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I was hoping you'd call. You might be ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 因为你有些 关于自己行为的全新 深刻见解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? Because you have some new and profound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要分享\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}insights you'd like to share on your behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更准确的是我想你的声音了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More like I missed your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几周很疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been a crazy couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是打来问你 今晚什么时候回来我爸家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just calling to see what time you're coming to my dad's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以为你不希望我去 - 我不希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't think you wanted me to go. - I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们每年都去 今年也邀请了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we go every year and you were invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 小蕾 你还没告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit, Reggie. You haven't told him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 因为这事应该当面说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, because it should be in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且爸在明尼阿波利斯的诊所 我不想打扰他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Dad's in Minneapolis at the clinic. I didn't want to bother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你仍希望我们能和好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you're still hoping we can work it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是在异想天开 真的想太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're delusional, like, truly delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我是乐观主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'm an optimist?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你是希望我会原谅你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe you're hoping that I'll forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就不用继续当坏人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that you don't have to be the bad guy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞砸了 不意味着以后都如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fucked up. Doesn't mean it has to be forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fucked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸说的是钥匙锁在车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking up is locking your keys in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸说的是把电影票落在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking up is leaving your theater tickets at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的“好事”根本不能用这个词形容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does not begin to describe what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我们做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you've done to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯 如果你曾看过心理医生 或是读过自助书籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith, if you'd ever been to therapy, or read a self-help book,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或上网搜过“我为什么是大混蛋”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or googled, "Why am I such a fucking asshole,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你就会明白 为什么我们不可能和好如初\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then maybe you'd understand why there's no fixing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了件糟糕的事 但我爱你 我爱我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did a terrible thing, but I love you. I love our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你希望我去看心理医生 我会去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want me to go to therapy, I'll go to therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯 今晚我会告诉父亲我要离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keith, tonight I'm going to tell my father that I'm ending my marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你加入这次谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are welcome to be a part of that conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算捂住你的嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蕾 他知道 你会和我离婚只可能是因为我出轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reggie, he knows the only reason you'd end our marriage is if I cheated on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离婚是因为你 而他怎么想是我不能控制的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ended our marriage and I can't control what he thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次对话毫无意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This conversation was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你到底会不会去  - 是 我会去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you gonna be there or not? - Yeah. I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚点见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.81,0:24:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客 请注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attention, passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信 传说中的比利三棍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe it. Billy fucking Three-Sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.94,0:24:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索罗门格朗吉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Solomon Grungy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上那么多车站 偏偏啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of all the terminals in the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.66,0:24:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的袋子里装着什么 是尸体吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you got in that bag? Is there a body in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.08,0:24:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我认识的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:25:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曲棍球训练 只有皇后区有免费冰场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hockey practice. Only free ice is in Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.71,0:25:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗 尼基怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing? How's Nicky?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.75,0:25:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么每次有人遇见我 总是要问尼基怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is it that every time someone sees me, they ask how Nicky's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.21,0:25:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒暄而已 只是表示礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a pleasantry. That's all. Half-assed, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.13,0:25:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我只是想知道 乐队解散后你们过得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. I just want to know how y'all are surviving without the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼基没联系你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nicky hasn't reached out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.43,0:25:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 他为什么会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Why would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚在唐希尔有演出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We booked a gig at Don Hill's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐队重聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Getting the band back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.90,0:25:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为“从无到有”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calling it Ex Nihilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.65,0:25:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有海报 天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a flyer? Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个烂主意 名字更烂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is a shitty idea, with an even shittier name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.91,0:25:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的名字也加进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put you on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.24,0:25:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月4日 索尔 我有计划了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fourth of July, Sol. I got plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.45,0:25:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 重要计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi. - Big plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.45,0:25:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是吗  - 是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地铁站拉客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cruising the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚去吧 也许你会有惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show up tonight. You might be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.71,0:25:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是比利三棍 你应该介绍我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was Billy Three-Sticks. You could've introduced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.97,0:25:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.47,0:25:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.99,0:26:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过不再打给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You agreed you wouldn't call me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.45,0:26:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我不是怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry, I'm not pregnant or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事关重要 不过必须当面谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's important, and it has to be in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不太方便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now's not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.50,0:26:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那么今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Well, then, later tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.83,0:26:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我得去我岳父家参加一个派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight I have to go to a party at my father-in-law's,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.75,0:26:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到时候一定会得知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where he'll undoubtedly discover
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背着他的女儿和一个大学生出轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I cheated on his daughter with a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.92,0:26:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 在派对前见我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Meet me before the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.42,0:26:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上9点在唐希尔 春街和格林尼治街 是个夜店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don Hill's at 9:00 p.m. Spring and Greenwich. It's a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.47,0:26:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们没什么可聊的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we have nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.85,0:26:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果你不来见我 那我只能去找你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. If you don't come to me, then I'm gonna have to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.85,0:26:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎 别这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Samantha, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次去大都会时 你指给我看是哪栋楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You showed me where the building was that time we went to the Met.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别这么做 求求你 请远离我和我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't do that. Please. Please, stay away from me and my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.36,0:26:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说了 给你老婆字条的不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already told you, I'm not the one who sent that note to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.98,0:26:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得我知道是谁给的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think that I might know who did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.32,0:26:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人不希望我们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are people who don't want us to be together and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.28,0:27:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前没告诉你 因为我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't tell you before because I didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.41,0:27:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我开始懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now I'm starting to,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.54,0:27:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很担心会发生不好的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'm really worried that something bad is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.25,0:27:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不好的事已经发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, something bad has already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么比毁了我的婚姻更糟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can be worse than blowing up my marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了其他的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blowing up something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.60,0:27:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(易燃 远离火源)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.28,0:27:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂  - 嘿 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello? - Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, something has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.24,0:27:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚得去看一个乐队的演出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I kind of need to see this band tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.46,0:27:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我的乐队 只不过少了我和其他重要的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my band actually, minus me and anyone else that fucking matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.34,0:27:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们要去巴特利公园看烟火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we were going to Battery Park to watch the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.26,0:28:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 和我一起去吧...拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, come with me. Come with me. Come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.05,0:28:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我必须得去看他们演出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Babe? I can't not be there for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.89,0:28:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得亲眼看看这场闹剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to see this fucking travesty unfold with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 我感觉不太舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I'm feeling just a little under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.48,0:28:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身疼 像流感 你读过关于SARS的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Achy, fluey. Have you read about SARS?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.65,0:28:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不想传染别人 - 我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I wouldn't wanna infect anyone. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.70,0:28:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有得SARS 墨瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do not have SARS, Merce.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.49,0:28:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 行 你就留在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine. Just stay home,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.87,0:28:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾好自己 多喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}be good to yourself and drink lots of fluids.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回头见 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll see you later. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.63,0:28:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜拜 - 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.44,0:28:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(威廉哈密尔顿斯维尼先生及夫人)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.99,0:29:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(邀请您参加鸡尾酒会 庆祝7月4号国庆日)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.34,0:29:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.35,0:29:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you ready for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.48,0:29:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我什么都准备好了 一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. I'm ready for anything. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.82,0:29:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带票了吗 还是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So do you have the tickets, or--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.41,0:29:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么票 地铁票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tickets for what? For the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前事追溯的票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Ex Post Facto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:29:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是歌剧表演 小白 没有门票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the opera, rookie. There are no tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.92,0:29:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在他们叫从无到有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also, it's Ex Nihilo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.92,0:30:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天 没了我 你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, what did you do without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 抱歉 你能等下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, sorry. Can you hold on?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.09,0:30:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能等下吗 我得... - 快点 地铁20分钟后出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you wait? I need to-- - Hurry up. Our train's in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.39,0:30:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 地铁20分钟后出发 - 抱歉 我马上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Our train's in 20 minutes. - Sorry, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.73,0:30:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 威尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.31,0:30:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.65,0:30:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了  - 桑托斯太太在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Mrs. Santos is on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.86,0:30:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法律上 是由她负责 但你能不能帮忙看下妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Legally, she's in charge, but can you just keep an eye on your sister, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.20,0:30:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 快看那鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guys, look at the bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.33,0:30:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 凯特 好漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow, Cate. That is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.09,0:30:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会去派对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Dad gonna be at the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.80,0:30:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 计划如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和他复合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get back together with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.18,0:30:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔 你知道你爸很爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will, you know that your dad loves you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.77,0:31:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这一切与你们无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And none of this has anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.81,0:31:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是就是吧 帮我向外公问好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No shit. Say hi to Grandpa for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.65,0:31:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}N--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.91,0:31:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你的相机在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, so, where's your camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.12,0:31:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定想为你的杂志 记录乐队复合的时刻吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, surely you're gonna wanna document the band's reunion for your zine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.54,0:31:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相机不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Camera's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.54,0:31:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit. What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.84,0:31:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我知道 就不叫“不见了” 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I knew that, it wouldn't be missing, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不过 是你弄丢了还是被人拿走了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. But, you lost it, or someone took it, or--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.34,0:31:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 查尔斯 我说了 不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ, Charles. I said I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.85,0:31:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是运河街\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next stop is Canal Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨 你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.41,0:31:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 你是唯一这么问过我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you're the only one who ever asks me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.80,0:32:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(唐希尔)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.80,0:32:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没有身份证 - 你不需要 你和我一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't have ID. - You don't need an ID. You're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.97,0:32:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 我就知道今晚会见到你 小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi. - I knew we'd be seeing you tonight, Sammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.77,0:32:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这瘦竹竿是谁  - 这是查尔斯 我的学徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who's the beanpole? - This is Charles, my protégé.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.81,0:32:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 别品头论足 他还在进步中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi. - Don't judge. He's a work in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友就是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friends are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就希望你这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was hoping you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.19,0:32:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯 你自己一个人待一小时没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles, do you think you would be okay on your own for an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.53,0:32:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得去上城区 - 小萨 搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have to go uptown. - What the fuck, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.11,0:32:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你想今晚和我一起过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you wanted to spend tonight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.62,0:32:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 我真的想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.28,0:32:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...我得解决一个问题 非常紧急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just-- There's a problem that I have to deal with, and it can't really wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.58,0:32:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我一小时后没回来 就来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm not back in an hour, come find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.00,0:32:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公园旁 第五大道和73街路口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the park, 5th and 73rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.21,0:32:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.08,0:33:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.30,0:33:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 你真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, you look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.97,0:33:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这派对好奢华 恭喜你 菲莉希亚 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fabulous party. Congratulations, Felicia. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.39,0:33:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸在哪 我想听他说说他的诊断结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Daddy? I want to hear how everything went at the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健康方面是好消息 他所有测试都通过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Healthwise, the news is good. He passed all his tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.65,0:33:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是失智症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's not dementia?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.15,0:33:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他目前的状况下什么都不需要改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's holding at a level where nothing needs to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.99,0:33:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很高兴这不会影响工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's very pleased this won't affect work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.95,0:33:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 请为他感到高兴 - 我会的 他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please be happy for him. - I will. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.91,0:34:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧 明尼阿波利斯有雷电风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, there was a lightning storm in Minneapolis,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G4不能飞 所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the G4 is grounded, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.70,0:34:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那帅哥老公呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your handsome husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.92,0:34:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在路上 应该很快就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming. Soon, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.00,0:34:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该告诉你 我们要分开...我们已经分开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should probably tell you that we're separating-- That we have separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.76,0:34:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这是不是 你的艾莫里叔叔找你的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm wondering if this is why your Uncle Amory is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.80,0:34:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道艾莫里怎么会得知消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't know how Amory would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没告诉任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We haven't told anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.43,0:34:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的 艾莫里总有办法得知一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Amory has a way of finding out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.93,0:34:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 见到你真好 - 是 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fabulous to see you. - Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找艾莫里叔叔吧 他很坚持 今晚一定要和你聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do find Uncle Amory. He's adamant about speaking with you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.36,0:34:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你站在别人的外套上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're standing on someone's jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.05,0:34:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我一直在观察你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.97,0:34:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的舞姿 什么都不在乎的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like how you dance, like you don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.47,0:35:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.68,0:35:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你有携带吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, are you holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.68,0:35:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论你嗑了什么 我都想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause whatever you're on, I definitely want some.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.40,0:35:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚嗑完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. Fresh out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.19,0:35:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 原本一定不会浪费你的货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bummer. Would have made it worth your while.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.49,0:35:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 演出结束后 我可以带你去后台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I could probably get you backstage after the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.82,0:35:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和乐队一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm with the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.91,0:35:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.87,0:35:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.13,0:35:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.44,0:35:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄铜战术 总有代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brass tactics This shit's never free
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.15,0:36:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都在 各取所需\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody's inside Taking what they need
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.28,0:36:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受诅咒的天主教徒 把那募捐桶给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Curse Catholics Now pass me that collection basket
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.49,0:36:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现金小费给我 来者不拒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd take the cash tip Any day of the week
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.83,0:36:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ooh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.75,0:36:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ooh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.55,0:36:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄铜战术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brass tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.72,0:36:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大众去死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck the masses
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.11,0:36:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 老板 到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, boss. We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.65,0:36:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不...就继续开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, no-- Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.53,0:36:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续开 别停就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep going. Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.15,0:36:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 我不是... - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, no, I'm not-- I'm, I wasn't-- - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.50,0:36:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我以为你在等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologies. I thought you were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在等 不过不是等车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm waiting, just not for the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.21,0:37:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不确定自己在等什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not exactly sure what I'm waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.09,0:37:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等某个迹象 我总是在等那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A sign, maybe? That's what I'm always waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.97,0:37:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如让我当你的迹象 你可以当我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about I be yours? You can be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.94,0:37:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们安心认定 这就是我们此刻该身处的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just be reassured that we are exactly where we are supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.15,0:37:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要坐在这个长凳上 不挪屁股\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I am going to keep my butt firmly rooted to this bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走到街道那边 进入未知世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will cross the street into an unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.33,0:37:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生只有一次 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You only live once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.75,0:37:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就够了 只要没有白活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once is enough, if you do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.56,0:37:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是国内最古老战舰的甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the deck of the country's oldest battleship,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.65,0:37:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老铁壳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Ironsides,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.48,0:37:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往神奇王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the Magic Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.56,0:38:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自上百个国家的数千移民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}thousands of immigrants from more than a hundred nations
