Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.78,0:45:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我该去找她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God. I should go meet up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.99,0:45:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概在等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's probably waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.08,0:45:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who the fuck was that guy? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.26,0:45:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你过来 比利 这意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for coming down, Billy. It means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.31,0:45:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和威廉算什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's the deal with you and William?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.35,0:45:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- “算什么”  - 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- "Deal"? - Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.52,0:45:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的弟弟 你们同居吗 是认真交往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's my brother. Do you live together? Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.73,0:45:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是的 对威廉来说是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is to me. Is it to William?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.70,0:45:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.45,0:45:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很多事都藏在心里 他的过去 家人 感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He keeps so much to himself. His past, his family, his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说话不经大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's careless with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.92,0:45:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认识的第一晚就说他爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Told me he loved me on the first night we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.92,0:45:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他知道那不是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he knew it wouldn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.71,0:46:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是典型威廉做派\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's classic William.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.18,0:46:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你不能说他从没说过这句话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you can't say he never said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.18,0:46:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永远都不会知道他说那话的真正意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can never know what he means by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.93,0:46:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So why'd you come here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.10,0:46:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道这会惹火他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I knew it would piss him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.65,0:46:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么邀请我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd you invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.65,0:46:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.24,0:46:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.40,0:47:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.70,0:47:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.67,0:47:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.89,0:47:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.85,0:47:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根汉密尔顿斯维尼兰普莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan Hamilton-Sweeney Lamplighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.61,0:47:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个牛人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are a badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.78,0:47:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把兰普莱特去掉 我已经不再用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please drop the "Lamplighter." I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.28,0:47:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别评判我 我几乎不碰这东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't judge me. I hardly ever touch this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.28,0:47:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.75,0:47:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是烟花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That must be the fireworks,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.46,0:47:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说菲莉希亚的表演很快就开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means Felicia's show is starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.92,0:48:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这绝对是枪声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Those were definitely gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.79,0:48:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是上东区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's the Upper East Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.96,0:48:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来自南部 我们懂枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm from the South. We know guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.26,0:48:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血止住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bleeding stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.76,0:48:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的痛苦要开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's time for the real pain to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.72,0:48:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的继叔叔艾莫里召唤我见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My step-uncle, Amory, has summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.10,0:48:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是威廉和我过去 给他起的绰号:恶魔弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or as William and I used to call him: the demon brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.77,0:48:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.61,0:48:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 能明白为什么威廉远离家人 - 需要帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can see why William stays away. - Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.73,0:48:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不用 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.65,0:48:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 邀请函写了“白色” - 白色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The invitation said "white." - White.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.53,0:48:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他穿了米黄色 而那完全是灰色...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then he's wearing beige, and that's fully gray--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.95,0:48:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉 抱歉...莉莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Lily, sorry. Sorry, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.91,0:48:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 你没事 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, you're good. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.46,0:48:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.17,0:48:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.29,0:48:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 我的生命之光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.80,0:48:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于见到我最爱的 光芒四射的继侄女了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finally, I'm basking in the glow of my favorite step-niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.51,0:48:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莫里谷尔德 这位是墨瑟古德曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amory Gould, allow me to introduce Mercer Goodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.22,0:48:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古德曼先生 我不知道蕾根带了客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Goodman. I wasn't aware Regan was bringing a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.69,0:49:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恢复得很快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bounce back quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.94,0:49:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在学校认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know each other from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.81,0:49:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A student?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.02,0:49:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 但我也是作家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Teacher, but I'm also a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.48,0:49:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写过我可能拜读过的作品吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you written anything I might have read?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.19,0:49:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小说 纪实小说 《纽约客》的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A novel, roman à clef, perhaps a piece in the New Yorker?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.99,0:49:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得承认我并非每一期 都会读到虚构小说那一栏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must admit I don't get to the fiction in every issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.66,0:49:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很喜欢里面的插画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I do love the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.16,0:49:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没写过任何你可能读过的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't written anything you might have read,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.37,0:49:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或任何人读过的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or anybody else for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我打算很快做到这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm planning to soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.22,0:49:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 他真惹人喜欢 他很乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regan, he's delightful. He's so full of optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.63,0:49:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾几何时也自称为作家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I too once considered myself a bit of a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜的是我的产出大部分是粪土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, what I churned out was mostly excrement
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.81,0:49:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面点缀了一些未能消化的珠玉 勉强可以算是妙语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}studded with a few indigestible kernels of what once passed for wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.19,0:49:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道 把我的笔记本烧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know, setting my notebooks aflame...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.19,0:49:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我意识到自己是成年人的一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was the moment when I realized I was an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.66,0:50:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 抱歉 失陪 认识你很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. Excuse me. It's very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.50,0:50:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.59,0:50:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁比你更擅长打击人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knows how to dismantle a person quite like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.80,0:50:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾根 这话从你嘴里说出来 简直可以说是在夸赞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, coming from you, Regan, that almost seems like a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.55,0:50:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.59,0:50:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我们得聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. We have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.60,0:50:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 聊什么  - 你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- About what? - About your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.97,0:50:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 他通过了测试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. He passed his tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.97,0:50:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 令人大松一口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it was a great relief,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.43,0:50:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在他面临官司的当口 这并不是什么好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's not really much of a benefit when it's time for him to stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.61,0:50:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“官司”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, "trial"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.23,0:50:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法委婉地说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no way to sugarcoat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.57,0:50:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 你父亲下飞机后将被逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow, when your father gets off the plane, he's going to be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.86,0:50:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为什么被逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrested for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.91,0:50:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融罪 为了避税对若干资产估值过低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Financial crimes. Undervaluing certain assets for tax purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.70,0:50:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了取得贷款对资产估值过高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Overvaluing them to secure loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.25,0:50:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银行向联邦调查局举报了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bank blew the whistle to the feds.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.17,0:50:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸绝不会这么做的 一定是搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy would never. It's some kind of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.21,0:50:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是别人犯的错 - 支票上是他的签名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Someone else's wrongdoing. - His signature is on the checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.34,0:50:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房产文件上是他的姓 如果他们收回一栋 就能收回全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's his family name on the buildings. If they take one, they can take them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.76,0:51:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为他的女儿和这间公司的首席营运官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, as his daughter and the COO of this company,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.10,0:51:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你给此事定下基调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we need you to set the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.98,0:51:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我明天会安排一些 值得信任的顾问碰头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right? I'm gonna gather a few trusted advisers tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.27,0:51:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要定好一些关键说辞 我们需要统一战线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna set up some bullet points. We need a united front.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.01,0:51:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.26,0:51:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.87,0:52:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.62,0:52:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anybody in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.05,0:52:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.35,0:52:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.44,0:52:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮忙...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.16,0:52:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是 我需要帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? Yes, I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.00,0:52:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央公园发生了枪击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's been a shooting in Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.25,0:52:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在第五大道和70多号街的路口 在东侧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm off of 5th and seventy-something, on the East Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.80,0:52:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 请尽快赶来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, can you just come as soon as you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.63,0:53:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.40,0:53:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮忙 快来帮帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help! Anyone, please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.72,0:53:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.22,0:53:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萨 醒醒 小萨 拜托 小萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sam, wake up. Sam, come on, please. Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.62,0:54:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.84,0:55:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(纽约警察)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.26,0:55:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(消防局)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.92,0:55:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.80,0:55:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在公园做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you doing in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.97,0:55:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. I wasn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.56,0:56:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等巴士 然后我听见某个声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was waiting for the bus, and I heard a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.61,0:56:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始以为是动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just thought it was an animal at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.52,0:56:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我走进公园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then when I walked into the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.32,0:56:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那时我看到了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's when I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.99,0:56:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没在附近看到其他人  - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You didn't see anyone else in the area? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.24,0:56:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 当时很暗... - 帕尔撒警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It was just really dark-- - Detective Parsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.91,0:56:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克法登 曼哈顿北区 看来这是刚遇害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}McFadden, Manhattan North. Looks like we caught a fresh one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.50,0:56:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.13,0:56:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是女孩身上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was on the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.63,0:56:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.76,0:56:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我猜这也是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well then, I suppose this is yours too?
